{"tid":1742302,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"爭議太多！ 德國電信：兩年內將華為零件全換掉","createTime":"2019-11-20T17:25:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T14:28:29.000Z","uid":141151,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"10b5031367a279cc7821547aa714ff599c9c4fa9","tid":1742302,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T17:25:46.000Z","msg":"爭議太多！ 德國電信：兩年內將華為零件全換掉<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2984580\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2984580&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzjcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=439c50d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2984580&h=bad65ed3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2984580</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕有消息指出，「德國電信」管理層表示，因為中國通訊業者華為的安全風險實在引發太多爭議，目前正使用的零件將逐漸更換，未來2年內將會把華為零件比例降到0。<br />\n<br />\n根據《德國之聲》報導，德國《商業週刊》掌握「德國電信」管理層的消息，指出未來2年內，目前正使用的華為零件將會被逐漸替換至0，而美國方面的元件也會被更換，德國電信強調，此舉是正常的元件更新。<br />\n<br />\n德國電信內部人士也透露，未來將會直接購買軟體公司「甲骨文」的產品，不會向華為購買包含軟體在內的「全套方案」。由於華為禁令的緣故，德國電信希望透過這樣的採購策略，確保獲得軟體的管道通暢。"},{"pid":"a7adadb6ab183cd290a23433f6969260a3aacdb5","tid":1742302,"uid":306826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T17:26:15.000Z","msg":"阻你地少少時間 有關選舉問題可以睇以下post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n0成本截斷建制藍絲收入 (下)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742026</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4993a414b2ea9b4c889fd62c483aef1f40c82321","tid":1742302,"uid":3522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T17:26:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75051782621621ed1783a6be810cdb723f4ca9d2","tid":1742302,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T17:27:51.000Z","msg":"終於生必"},{"pid":"5f1522